  <SUMMARY>
    LLMP (LLMemory Palace) v25 is a complete npm CLI package for neural code genome compression. 
    It provides algorithmic compression (no LLM required) with 50-2000x compression ratios, 
    supporting 15+ programming languages with one-line genome generation, CXML/JSON export, 
    and a beautiful CLI with sunshine rays ASCII art logo.
  </SUMMARY>

